TO circle
repeat 360 [forward 1 right 1] end
End

TO CIRCLE_AND_SQUARE
HOME
CLEAN
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
FORWARD 50
REPEAT 3 [LEFT 90 FORWARD 100]
LEFT 90
FORWARD 50
END

TO donut
repeat 360 [forward 4 square right 1]
end

to square
repeat 4 [forward 100 right 90]
End

to triangle
repeat 3 [forward 100 left 120]
end

